<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 rú guǒ méi yǒu zhǔ ài de chān fú, xiàng wǒ zěn néng zǒu dào tiān yá,
 rú guǒ méi yǒu shèng líng qí miào de yǐn dǎo, jiù méi yǒu lí jiā chū zǒu de bù fá.
 wèi le ràng quán qiú rén de yǎn jīng yǎng wàng zhǔ, dōu jīng lì le fēng chuī yǔ dǎ,
 bā bù dé yī yè zǒu biàn quán shì jiè, bǎ ài de zhǒng zi bō sā.
 zhǔ huì yǐn dǎo wǒ men qián xíng, zǒu de huì zǒu liú xià de jiù liú xià,
 wǒ men zhōng yú chéng wèi yíng jiā, yī dào lái fù xìng zhōng huá.</lyrics>
<title>zhōng yú chéng wèi yíng jiā 迦南548</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>548</hymn_number>
</song>